Class SearchController

java.lang.Object
controllers.SearchController
public class SearchController extends Object
Controller for searching photos by date range or tags. Produces a result album from search results and allows navigation back to the main view.

Search results may be persisted into a new album for the active user. Supports AND/OR semantics for tag searches.

Author:
Zach
